9. For "Location", extract explicit location information, including phrases referring to distance or place.
10. For "Amenity", extract any specific amenities or features requested (e.g., "childrens menu").
11. For "Price", extract any synonyms or explicit mentions of price level, such as "cheap", "inexpensive", or contextual phrases.

Remember to return *only* the JSON object, with no additional explanation or text.

