- Rating (e.g. "4 stars", "good reviews")
- Amenity (e.g. "buffet", "wifi", "outdoor seating")
- Location (any phrase indicating location or proximity, e.g. "on the parkway", "close by", "isnt too far away")
- Restaurant_Name (e.g. "Jasmine Bistros")
- Price (e.g. "cheap", "expensive", "pricing good", "pricing")
- Hours (any phrase or time indicating opening/closing times, e.g. "stays open late like after 10 pm")
- Dish (e.g. "pasta", "mango sticky rice")
- Cuisine (e.g. "italian", "mongolian bbq", "new mongolian bbq")

