- Rating: Any descriptor related to the quality or rating of restaurants (e.g., "best", "top rated", "best rated").
- Amenity: Any service, feature, or facility mentioned that the restaurant should offer (e.g., "drive thru", "outdoor seating", "wifi", "kid friendly", "delivery").
- Location: Any mention of a specified or implied geographic location, including city names or relative terms (e.g., "austin", "near me").

