- Extract and match the slot types exactly per the scheme above; do not introduce new or incorrect slot keys.
- For the "Location" slot, include not only specific addresses, streets, or neighborhoods, but also relative or proximity phrases (such as "near downtown", "in town", "nearest", and similar).
- For "Hours," extract full relevant phrases (e.g., "stays open late like after 10 pm") rather than paraphrasing or shortening unless the original phrase is redundant.
- For "Dish" extract only the name of the food item (like "hamburger", "sub") and not the name of the establishment ("sub shop" is incorrect for this slot).
- Do not use "Restaurant_Name" unless the user refers to a specific, proper name of a restaurant.
- Extract all relevant slot-value pairs mentioned in the user query; do not omit or invent slots or values.
- The extracted phrases should closely match (verbatim whenever possible) what the user expressed in the query.
- Only include as output the slot-value JSON as instructed; do not provide explanations or extra information.

